{"parse":{"title":"High Grade Build Divers","pageid":91679,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><figure class=\"thumb mw-halign-right show-info-icon\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\" style=\"width: 150px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/16/HGBDLogo.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180306015944\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"High Grade Build Divers Logo\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"112\" class=\"thumbimage lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGBDLogo.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGBDLogo.jpg\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/16/HGBDLogo.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20180306015944\" /></a> \t<noscript><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/16/HGBDLogo.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180306015944\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"High Grade Build Divers Logo\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/16/HGBDLogo.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20180306015944\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"112\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"HGBDLogo.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGBDLogo.jpg\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/16/HGBDLogo.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20180306015944\" /></a></noscript> \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:HGBDLogo.jpg\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">High Grade Build Divers Logo</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<figure class=\"thumb mw-halign-right show-info-icon\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\" style=\"width: 150px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/2/2e/SDBDLogo.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180929140845\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"SD Build Divers Logo\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"111\" class=\"thumbimage lazyload\" data-image-name=\"SDBDLogo.jpg\" data-image-key=\"SDBDLogo.jpg\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/2/2e/SDBDLogo.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20180929140845\" /></a> \t<noscript><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/2/2e/SDBDLogo.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180929140845\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"SD Build Divers Logo\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/2/2e/SDBDLogo.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20180929140845\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"111\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"SDBDLogo.jpg\" data-image-key=\"SDBDLogo.jpg\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/2/2e/SDBDLogo.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20180929140845\" /></a></noscript> \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:SDBDLogo.jpg\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">SD Build Divers Logo</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p><b>High Grade Build Divers (HGBD)</b><span style=\"font-weight: normal\"> (<span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\">\u30cf\u30a4\u30b0\u30ec\u30fc\u30c9\u30d3\u30eb\u30c9\u30c0\u30a4\u30d0\u30fc\u30ba</span><span class=\"t_nihongo_comma\" style=\"display:none\">,</span> <i><span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\">Hai Gur\u0113do Birudo Daib\u0101zu</span></i><span class=\"t_nihongo_help\"><sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Japanese\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Help:Japanese\"><span class=\"t_nihongo_icon\" style=\"color:#00e;font:bold 80% sans-serif;text-decoration:none;padding:0 .1em;\">?</span></a></sup></span>)</span> is a line of <a href=\"/wiki/Gunpla\" title=\"Gunpla\">Gunpla</a> kits of the <a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Weapon\" title=\"Mobile Weapon\">Mobile Suits</a> from the&#160;<i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Divers\" title=\"Gundam Build Divers\">Gundam Build Divers</a></i>&#160;series. It is split into two lines: the standard HG 1/144 model kits and <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Build_Custom\" title=\"High Grade Build Custom\">High Grade Build Custom</a>, which consists of accessories to enhance other Gunpla kits. The HGBD line also includes the sub-line <b>SD Build Divers (SDBD)</b> and <b>Figure-rise Standard BUILD DIVERS (FRSBD)</b>.\n</p><p>Following the reorganization of Bandai Namco Group, box covers of reissue and future release of kits from September 2018 onwards feature a blue Bandai logo instead of the original red logo, while releases and reissues from mid-2022 onwards feature the Bandai Namco logo on the upper left corner.\n</p>\n<div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Regulars_and_Special_Editions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Regulars and Special Editions</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Exclusives\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Exclusives</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Notes_&amp;_Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes &amp; Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Regulars_and_Special_Editions\">Regulars and Special Editions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FHigh_Grade_Build_Divers%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Gundam_Build_Divers_\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Gundam Build Divers </a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Gundam_Build_Divers_Break\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Gundam Build Divers Break</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Special_Editions_\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Special Editions </a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>HGBD #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th>\n<th>Link\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>000<figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/42/HGBD_Gundam_00_Diver.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180403170734\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGBD Gundam 00 Diver\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/42/HGBD_Gundam_00_Diver.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20180403170734\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"HGBD Gundam 00 Diver.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGBD_Gundam_00_Diver.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GN-0000DVR_Gundam_00_Diver\" title=\"GN-0000DVR Gundam 00 Diver\">GN-0000DVR Gundam 00 Diver</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Divers\" title=\"Gundam Build Divers\">Gundam Build Divers</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,000\n</td>\n<td>2018 April\n</td>\n<td>Uses the A and B plate runners of <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Gundam_00\" title=\"High Grade Gundam 00\">HG00-22</a>. Diver Ace Unit is sold separately as HGBC-036.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1015\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>001<figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/f/fb/HGBD_Gundam_AGEII_Magnum.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180309020626\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGBD Gundam AGEII Magnum\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/f/fb/HGBD_Gundam_AGEII_Magnum.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20180309020626\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"HGBD Gundam AGEII Magnum.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGBD_Gundam_AGEII_Magnum.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/AGE-IIMG_Gundam_AGEII_Magnum\" title=\"AGE-IIMG Gundam AGEII Magnum\">AGE-IIMG Gundam AGEII Magnum</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Divers\" title=\"Gundam Build Divers\">Gundam Build Divers</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,800\n</td>\n<td>2018 March\n</td>\n<td>First kit in the series. Transforms via parts-swapping. Includes clear BA-0 display base. Uses the A and D plate runners of <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Gundam_AGE\" title=\"High Grade Gundam AGE\">HGAGE-10</a>.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1025\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>002<figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/4a/HGBD_GM_III_Beam_Master.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20250307042734\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGBD GM III Beam Master\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/4a/HGBD_GM_III_Beam_Master.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20250307042734\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"HGBD GM III Beam Master.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGBD_GM_III_Beam_Master.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RGM-86RBM_GM_III_Beam_Master\" title=\"RGM-86RBM GM III Beam Master\">RGM-86RBM GM III Beam Master</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Divers\" title=\"Gundam Build Divers\">Gundam Build Divers</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,800\n</td>\n<td>2018 April\n</td>\n<td>Parts and color variant of <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Universal_Century\" title=\"High Grade Universal Century\">HGUC-126</a>.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1017\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>003<figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/3/37/HGBD_Grimoire_Red_Beret.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180418173528\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGBD Grimoire Red Beret\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGBD Grimoire Red Beret.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGBD_Grimoire_Red_Beret.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/3/37/HGBD_Grimoire_Red_Beret.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20180418173528\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GH-001RB_Grimoire_Red_Beret\" title=\"GH-001RB Grimoire Red Beret\">GH-001RB Grimoire Red Beret</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Divers\" title=\"Gundam Build Divers\">Gundam Build Divers</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,800\n</td>\n<td>2018 April\n</td>\n<td>Parts and color variant of <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Reconguista_in_G\" title=\"High Grade Reconguista in G\">HGRG-02</a>. Features transformable scissor claws. Includes two Minimoires. Tiltrotor Pack is sold separately as HGBC-037.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1016\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>004<figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/92/HGBD_Momokapool.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180514124401\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGBD Momokapool\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGBD Momokapool.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGBD_Momokapool.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/92/HGBD_Momokapool.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20180514124401\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/PEN-01M_Momokapool\" title=\"PEN-01M Momokapool\">PEN-01M Momokapool</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Divers\" title=\"Gundam Build Divers\">Gundam Build Divers</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,800\n</td>\n<td>2018 May\n</td>\n<td>First original kit in the series. Transformation into Ball Mode requires removal of arms. Includes Petitkapool with display base. Petitkapool transforms via parts-forming. Several runners are labeled \"Kapool\", which indicates that an HGCC <a href=\"/wiki/AMX-109_Kapool\" title=\"AMX-109 Kapool\">AMX-109 Kapool</a>/HGUC <a href=\"/wiki/AMX-109_Capule\" title=\"AMX-109 Capule\">AMX-109 Capule</a> is set for future release.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1018\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>005<figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/00/HGBD_Ogre_GN-X.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180514124432\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGBD Ogre GN-X\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"80\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGBD Ogre GN-X.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGBD_Ogre_GN-X.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/00/HGBD_Ogre_GN-X.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20180514124432\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GNX-803OG_Ogre_GN-X\" title=\"GNX-803OG Ogre GN-X\">GNX-803OG Ogre GN-X</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Divers\" title=\"Gundam Build Divers\">Gundam Build Divers</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,000\n</td>\n<td>2018 May\n<